INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (11, '“他的战术安排真的迷住了我！”', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<section style=\"margin: 10px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; justify-content: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 10px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; min-width: 10%; height: auto; border: 2px solid #add7f4;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">官网 &middot;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #6caddf;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">专访</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">前阿森纳球员，现足球评论员迪克森近日在接受曼城官网的采访时，认为坎塞洛和沃克的边后卫组合是上赛季曼城取得成功的关键。</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">迪克森出生在曼彻斯特，儿时支持的球队就是曼城。他在谈到瓜帅在边后卫上的排兵布阵时说：</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&ldquo;边后卫的职责和我当年已经不一样了。如果我说现在的边后卫不会防守，那我一定是个恐龙（老古董）了。他们当然会防守，只是防守的方式和责任有所不同。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">从很多方面来说这都是一个不太一样的位置，但是归根结底任务还是不让皮球滚进自家大门。有时候他们后防线四个球员平行站位，有时候边后卫会持球压上，更靠近中场区域，这些战术安排真的迷住了我。&rdquo;</span></strong></p>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">随后迪克森对于瓜帅的变阵能力评价到：</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&ldquo;我现在的工作就是分析和评论足球战术，如果瓜帅没有把他的想法注入足球，战术一尘不变，那么我的工作也就没什么意思了。</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">我球员时期和瓜迪奥拉交手过几次，但是作为教练我们还没有过交流，但是他对于足球的想法让我十分好奇。</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">我们一般都会有一个固定的战术思维，但是瓜帅总是在比赛中频繁对战术体系做出调整，他手下的边后卫的工作也会不断变化，我很喜欢这一点。这样球员也会有更强的适应性。&rdquo;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-