INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (13, '血染赛场，他舍身捍卫城门！', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<section style=\"margin: 10px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; justify-content: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 10px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; min-width: 10%; height: auto; border: 2px solid #add7f4;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">前曼城门将 &middot;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #6caddf;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">称赞</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #6caddf;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">埃德森</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">周末联赛，埃德森在开场不久被巴恩斯撞伤，血染赛场。经过简单处理后，埃德森依旧坚持比赛，他也得到了前曼城门将<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">大卫&middot;詹姆斯的称赞</span>：</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&ldquo;在埃德森加盟前，我曾经看过他在本菲卡队的录像。遇到危险，他会扑向进攻球员的脚下，他像狮子一样勇敢！&rdquo;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&ldquo;他就是这种风格的球员，今天的比赛他再次证明了这一点！如果当时他没有过人的勇气，或许莱斯特城很早就取得领先了。正是他无懈可击<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;\">的表现帮助曼城战胜了强悍的莱斯特城。&rdquo;</span></strong></span></p>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 10px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; justify-content: center;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 10px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; min-width: 10%; height: auto; border: 2px solid #add7f4;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">官网 &middot;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #6caddf;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">专访</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">德布劳内上周已经和球队一起参加训练。上周末的联赛，进入大名单的德布劳内最终并未出场，对此瓜帅表示：<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&ldquo;德布劳内在上周的训练中表现得很好，但他目前仍处于恢复状态，我并不急于让他上场。我们拥有福登、德布劳内、马赫雷斯、斯通斯这样的球员，阵容也有一定的厚度。在之前对阵诺维奇和阿森纳队的两场比赛，首发的球员表现得都很好，他们也值得继续首发。&rdquo;<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" /></span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&ldquo;没有参加比赛的球员也必须时刻做好准备，球队的整体实力是我们在此前几个赛季取得成功的原因，每个人都可以为球队贡献自己的力量。&rdquo;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">曼城将在周三迎战本赛季欧冠的首个对手&mdash;&mdash;RB莱比锡。尽管对阵巴黎圣日耳曼的比赛更引人关注，但瓜帅表示：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&ldquo;我们最艰难的比赛是对阵RB莱比锡的第一场欧冠，这是小组赛阶段最为重要的比赛，我现在不会去想巴黎圣日耳曼，因为我们的每个对手都很难缠。&rdquo;</strong></span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 48px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&ldquo;RB莱比锡近几年虽然没有给在联赛中势不可挡的拜仁造成太大的威胁，但他们与多特蒙德之间的竞争很激烈。我很清楚他们的实力，这场比赛对我们而言是一个考验，我会把对阵莱斯特城队的打法投入使用，并尝试踢出一场精彩的比赛。&rdquo;</span></strong></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<p><audio style=\"display: none;\" controls=\"controls\"></audio></p>\n</body>\n</html>', 'http://localhost:8080/upload/20210919_17284646.png', 1, '2021-09-19 17:28:48', 10);
