INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES (18, '他们这次回城，是为爱而战！', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei UI\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">今天凌晨，&ldquo;足球援助&rdquo;（Soccer Aid）慈善赛在阿提哈德球场打响。</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">英格兰队教练组由曼城功勋埃里克森、米卡&middot;理查兹和大卫&middot;希曼组成。前曼城球员大卫&middot;詹姆斯担任门将，赖特&middot;菲利普斯担任前锋。此外，英格兰队阵中还拥有加里&middot;内维尔、卡拉格、斯科尔斯、鲁尼、乔&middot;科尔等知名球星。</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">世界明星联队则由雷德克纳普担任主帅，球队阵中拥有</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">吉文、萨巴莱塔和德容三位曼城老将<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">。昔日球星罗伯特&middot;卡洛斯、埃弗拉、西多夫、弗莱彻以及短跑运动员博尔特也代表世界明星联队出场。</span></span></span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最终，世界明星联队3-0战胜了英格兰队。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这次活动一共为联合国儿童基金会筹集了超过1300万英镑的慈善款。</span></p>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', sans-serif; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"margin: 10px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; justify-content: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 10px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; min-width: 10%; height: auto; border: 2px solid #add7f4;\">\n<section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">曼城女足 &middot;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #6caddf;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">开门红</strong></span></p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n<section style=\"margin: 0px 32px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section>\n<section style=\"ma